Pregnancy:Advise female patients of childbearing age about the consequences of exposure to olmesartan medoxomil and hydrochlorothiazide during pregnancy. Discusstreatment options withwomenplanning to become pregnant.Tellpatients to reportpregnancies to their physiciansas soon as possible[see 


